welcome_message_body: Welcome to Putrajaya, Malaysia! This charming city is known for its stunning architecture, beautiful gardens, and picturesque waterfront. We invite you to explore and enjoy all that Putrajaya has to offer during your visit.

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: The main terminal at Kuala Lumpur International Airport, also known as KLIA, serves both domestic and international flights.

terminals.name: klia2 Terminal
terminals.description: The klia2 terminal at Kuala Lumpur International Airport is dedicated to low-cost carriers and budget airlines.

wifi.note: Passengers can enjoy free WiFi for up to 3 hours per day with unlimited data usage.

terminals.name: Terminal 1
terminals.description: The main terminal for domestic and international flights.

terminals.name: Terminal 2
terminals.description: A smaller terminal for domestic flights only.

wifi.note: Free WiFi is available throughout the airport.
